SlimHorizontalToolBar: Toolbar which is a slim version of the toolbar that aligns an icon and a text element horizontally
UniformToolBar: A toolbar that tries to arrange all toolbar items uniformly (supports only horizontal toolbars for now)
Menu: Vertical menu (pull-down menu, or context menu)
ButtonRow: Buttons arranged in rows, with a maximum number of buttons per row, like a toolbar but can have multiple rows
SlimHorizontalUniformToolBar: A toolbar with horizontally-oriented buttons that tries to arrange all toolbar items uniformly
